metadata.description:
Welcome! Either your friends or the fates have brought you to this ancient artifact. It's humming with a powerful energy, and seems to hold many secrets. Is it a key to a lost land? Does it unlock some treasure in the metaverse? Is it an invitation to an adventure? Or is it a map to a bigger prize worth collecting?
Perhaps this artifact is all of the above...and more.
In the next few weeks, prepare to receive some wonderful surprises! We canâ€™t wait to delight you with unexpected, enchanted gifts. Also, join our discord and let us know if you are able to unlock any of the mysterious messages encoded in this powerful artifact. discord.gg/xaZGmpRgRF
Credit: The lead artist for this artifact is the talented Ganesh Katave. You can find more information about him @ https://msha.ke/ganeshkatave/
